body:
Dear Riot,
As we all know, the Swain rework is coming up soon, and I had some suggestions for possible voice lines for our favorite Noxian birdman. Those of you in the comments, feel free to also give suggestions!
Taunt to {{champion:64}} : &quot;You remind me of something. A crow, perhaps....&quot;
Taunt to {{champion:7}}: &quot;The sharper the thorns, the more beautiful the rose.&quot;
{{champion:9}} : &quot;Hah! You cannot scare me away so easily!&quot;
{{champion:92}} and {{champion:141}} : &quot;You would betray your own blood and kin? You do not have the right to be called a Noxian.&quot;
{{champion:99}} : &quot;Your gifts are impressive. Why do you waste them on a superstitious horde?&quot;
{{champion:6}} : &quot;Hide in your gutter for now, Urgot. It will be laid waste to soon.&quot; 
{{champion:164}}/{{champion:254}}  and {{champion:51}}  : &quot;Not even you can save Piltover, Grey Lady/Enforcer.&quot;
{{champion:122}} : &quot;Varn was a traitor, boy. You would do well to forget her.&quot;
{{champion:110}}/{{champion:266}}  : Ah, another Darkin. You will regret opposing Noxus.
{{champion:143}}: "I always hated flowers, but after seeing you, I hate them even more... " (Thanks for that one, Zatsukino!)





And that&#039;s all for now! Again, any suggestions and feedback are appreciated!
Regards,
TheGreatRasputin.

